header.gameNote: WEST COAST CONFERENCE MEN'S TOURNAMENT - FINAL

videos.description: Killian Tillie sinks his 12th 3-pointer in the WCC tournament for Gonzaga, which nears the record of 15 consecutive.
videos.headline: Tillie sinks 12th consecutive 3-pointer for Gonzaga

videos.description: Josh Perkins Eurosteps around his defender and lays it in to extend Gonzaga's lead going into halftime.
videos.headline: Perkins finishes half with buzzer beater layup for Gonzaga

videos.description: Killian Tillie uses perfect form to sink another 3-pointer and the Gonzaga fans love it.
videos.headline: Tillie stays hot from behind the arc for Gonzaga

videos.description: Johnathan Williams finds Killian Tillie underneath the basket and he elevates for the jumper for Gonzaga.
videos.headline: Tillie makes tough and-1 shot

videos.description: Gonzaga wins the WCC title over BYU and has punched their ticket to the NCAA tournament.
videos.headline: Gonzaga clinches 20th straight NCAA tourney berth

videos.description: Killian Tillie says Gonzaga wanted to prove they were the best team in the conference and want to continue to prove themselves this month.
videos.headline: Tillie excited for what March will bring
